# Pillar2Spectral Module

Main entry point for PILAR 2: ANÁLISIS ESPECTRAL

This module provides the spectral analysis framework for the Riemann Hypothesis proof.

## Files

- `spectral_theorem.lean`: Spectral theorem for unbounded operators
- `H_psi_operator.lean`: Berry-Keating operator H_Ψ
- `trace_formula.lean`: Regularized trace formula
- `spectral_bijection.lean`: Bijection between spectrum and zeros
